  <Apparel_DeadlifePack.verbs.deploy_deadlife_dust.label>死の塵を展開</Apparel_DeadlifePack.verbs.deploy_deadlife_dust.label>
  
  <!-- EN: disruptor flare pack -->
  <Apparel_DisruptorFlarePack.label>妨害フレアパック</Apparel_DisruptorFlarePack.label>
  <!-- EN: A utility pack that shoots disruptor flares. On impact, the flare burns a capsule of bioferrite, which creates a bright flash and a local psychic disruption. This stuns psychically sensitive creatures, revealing those that are invisible, and reducing their consciousness and movement speed for a short while. Afterwards, the flare continues to burn, lighting up a wide area for some time. -->
  <Apparel_DisruptorFlarePack.description>妨害フレアを射出するユーティリティパック.フレアは着弾時にバイオフェライトのカプセルを燃焼させ,まばゆい閃光と局所的な精神混乱を引き起こします.これにより,敏感な精神を持つ生物はスタンし,不可視の生物はその姿が明らかになり,短時間その意識と移動速度が低下します.その後,フレアは燃焼を続け,一定時間広範囲を照らします.</Apparel_DisruptorFlarePack.description>
